metadata.name: BunnyBats #1
metadata.description: BunnyBats are fun cosmic creatures that come from the land of mystic unity. These playful illustrations depict a race of bunny souls as they undergo a process of evolution and awakening. In this universe, each bunny is taught a sacred truth; all sentient beings carry the seed of enlightenment. The sacredness of life's gift lays in cultivating one's innate creativity and magical power. We are one
